## Conditionals


::: {.cell hash='control_flow_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-1_91843dcf0d9639ec8fa7c4de96fc1bb1'}

```{.r .cell-code}
test_sign <- function(x) {
  if (x > 0) {
    "x is positif"
  } else if (x < 0) {
    "x is negatif"
  } else {
    "x is equal to zero"
  }
}
```
:::

::: {.cell hash='control_flow_cache/html/unnamed-chunk-2_c790db145d3098c01d3112415ee68ba1'}

```{.r .cell-code}
test_sign(3)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "x is positif"
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
test_sign(-2)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "x is negatif"
```
:::

```{.r .cell-code}
test_sign(0)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
```
[1] "x is equal to zero"
```
:::
:::


## Loops


